  <brief_title>Thrombophilic Risk Factors in Pediatric Patients Diagnosed at the Ha'Emek Medical Center</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Study Will Summarize the Clinical and Laboratory Data of All the Pediatric Patients Diagnosed With Thrombotic Events at the Pediatric Hematology Unit</official_title>
