  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will assess the clinical and laboratory data of about 100 pediatric patients
      diagnosed and treated at the Pediatric Hematology Unit during the years 1980 until 2007
      because of thrombotic events.

      The results, the treatment given, and the outcome of the patients will be summarized.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
